imdb.title: Bloodbath and Beyond
plot: _Bloodbath and Beyond_ (qv) is a crude, blunt, horror movie review show that reviews low budget indie flicks through studio films. Every week the trio discuss their favorite kills, the plot holes, and of course the gratuitous nudity.::Jay Bond
